dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:50,000 scale maps of North Korea, titled 'Chosen 1:50,000 Chikeizu/朝鮮五萬分之一地形圖: 1:50,000 Topo of Korea.' To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford Unviersity Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
